title: NFL ATL: Week 17 recap
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 17 recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Kevin Patra -- recap all of the Week 17 action including the “Sunday Night Football” matchup between the Philadelphia Eagles and Dallas Cowboys. Don’t miss the key takeaways and analysis from each game. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
